{
  "stem": "11179.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I saw them inside, the way they were-- the way they were treated by their officers-- very badly.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So whatever happened then, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "That's history.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'd see officers treated their-- treated their men like dogs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I didn't quite understand how they talked to them and so on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was-- it was obviously they were mis-- they were not treated very nicely, OK.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember many details.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, my God, they treat them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's what I remember-- how they treat them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was once inside a warehouse there, where the-- where the Chinese were stationed before they shipped them up there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- they weren't very well treated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And obviously, they were not-- not enthusiastic followers of Chiang Kai-shek anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And within-- Chiang Kai-shek was a big hero when the war was over when-- when-- among the Chinese in Shanghai.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a big VE Day, I remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then Chiang Kai-shek started to have universal military draft.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the Chinese soldier was, up to that time, regarded as a-- as very low, right above the beggar, the professional soldier.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the Chinese didn't like that at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "What was worse is that-- that a lot of the Chinese army, they came to town to amuse themselves on weekends or on the day off.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And movie theaters were limited in Shanghai, for instance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they forced their way into the crowded movie theaters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was a fire department there that didn't allow anybody to stand just like here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But they-- they were shooting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And later, they took their guns away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I understand they sold even hand grenades in some of the theaters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So they were very, very much unliked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And naturally, they blamed Chiang Kai-shek.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Right or wrong, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
